Sub/Context version 1.00
========================

Sub::Context allows you to control subroutine dispatch based on calling
context.  See the documentation.

To install this module, type:

   $ perl Build.PL
   $ ./Build
   $ ./Build test
   # ./Build install

You can also use the generated Makefile.PL, but I don't.

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires two libraries to run the tests:

	Test::More version 0.60 or better
	Test::Exception

